{"tid":2165578,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"毛上身巡淮河 公安扮災民  習做騷遮遲鈍","createTime":"2020-08-20T02:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T02:21:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bca94a2a5fc79cdcc405a86ddbad5906666d5c17","tid":2165578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:14:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/OXRPBEATZJCKZCIBBHSBL4ENC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FOXRPBEATZJCKZCIBBHSBL4ENC4%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=79553b72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FOXRPBEATZJCKZCIBBHSBL4ENC4%2F&h=02a2c3ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/OXRPBEATZJCKZCIBBHSBL4ENC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n毛上身巡淮河 公安扮災民 <br />\n習做騷遮遲鈍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tY1NffkxDfn3mvh3JcdQX4vOz7w=/2443x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y5J26OIZBVGZPIBQBGQTTRQNZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtY1NffkxDfn3mvh3JcdQX4vOz7w%3D%2F2443x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY5J26OIZBVGZPIBQBGQTTRQNZA.jpg&h=78b404d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平前日到上月洪災嚴重的安徽視察，新華社引用毛澤東當年號召「一定要把淮河修好」作報道。惟習探訪的一名災民卻被發現與當地一名治安副隊長極為相似，遭質疑用「臨演災民」。學者表示，習視察「遲到」的訊息相當明確，需用上「臨演」營造和諧，及扯上毛的歷史權威來裝飾。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：水淹樂山大佛腳趾 70年來首次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tY1NffkxDfn3mvh3JcdQX4vOz7w=/2443x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y5J26OIZBVGZPIBQBGQTTRQNZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtY1NffkxDfn3mvh3JcdQX4vOz7w%3D%2F2443x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY5J26OIZBVGZPIBQBGQTTRQNZA.jpg&h=78b404d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習近平前日在安徽阜陽視察淮河，被指仿效毛澤東。新華社<br />\n<br />\n各大官媒昨均重點報道習近平赴安徽視察的情況，指習一直牽掛災民。習稱「愚公移山、大禹治水，中華民族同自然災害鬥了幾千年，積累了寶貴經驗，我們還要繼續鬥下去」，。。。。。。。。。。惟其中一名與習近平對話的「災民」，被網民揭發與當地治安大隊副隊長閆靜極為相似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JD__TOAei_xTw2MY8sfXRKPZakI=/1384x922/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LGILOHIVPZFTJC3VGMJ34O7E4Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJD__TOAei_xTw2MY8sfXRKPZakI%3D%2F1384x922%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLGILOHIVPZFTJC3VGMJ34O7E4Y.gif&h=0edeaf3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一名與習近平對話的「災民」與當地治安副隊長極為相似。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刻意到安徽 將李克強軍<br />\n<br />\n新華社亦為習視察撰專題〈鑑往知來，跟着總書記學歷史〉，引述1951年毛澤東號召「一定要把淮河修好」、「持續開展大規模治淮建設，取得舉世矚目的輝煌成就」。<br />\n<br />\n政治學者吳強對本報表示，習近平在水災過後才出現，「遲鈍的訊息其實非常強烈的」，習現須展示親民印象，所以不論是「臨演災民」或引用毛澤東治河口號，都是為了裝飾遲。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n整個6、7月長江流域水災受災省分眾多，習選擇到國務院總理李克強故鄉安徽視察，吳強也稱「將軍」意味甚濃。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新華社/Twitter/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"9a7d36d413c175daf208726ac484788115c80523","tid":2165578,"uid":175930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"咁猛太陽先去巡<br />\n我真係笑咗出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}